text: Hello There! I am coming from a Television background and trying to transfer my Creative/Story Producer skill set to Branded Content. I've created over 100 hours of television and my work has spanned networks like: MTV, Bravo, VH1, Food Network, Discovery Plus and more. I take a multifaceted approach: I am constantly working on new development concepts, on-going productions, and current edits for content already filmed. As a 'Senior Story Producer' I am looking at the individual character and creating compelling story points around their journey, if I'm given a concept I am casting authentic people and following their stories, connecting them to the brand.
